OL,5, A Twitter employee has appealed to Elon
OL,6, Musk on the platform to ask whether he 
OL,7, had been sacked.                       
OL,9,FIn a tweet to the firm's chief         
OL,10,Fexecutive, Mr Thorleifsson said: "Your 
OL,11,Fhead of HR is not able to confirm if I 
OL,12,Fam employed or not".                   
OL,14,FMr Musk responded by asking: "What work
OL,15,Fhave you been doing?"                  
OL,17,FHalli Thorleifsson told the BBC that   
OL,18,Fnine days after being frozen out of    
OL,19,FTwitter's accounts he did not know     
OL,20,Fwhether he had been fired or not.      
